**Example 1: 删除Kafka导入配置**

删除Kafka导入配置

Input: 

```
tccli cls DeleteKafkaRecharge --cli-unfold-argument  \
    --Id 06bdb6f6-ae6e-41f6-9e7b-fcab91cb0895 \
    --TopicId 1014cc79-f006-48e4-8820-1dc727054111
```

Output: 
```
{
    "Response": {
        "RequestId": "00a1e648-bea8-4f85-8a7c-71f84169f207"
    }
}
```
